eight new Titan Portraits as additional avatars. These include Zeus, Poseidon, Athena, Odin, Thor, Loki, Runa and Valwen.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https:\/\/lh4.googleusercontent.com\/OobFwjfkXVg3nofuUT7MqIHn4jYfaH-NlW1hBUXNudHFUe2Gdy74gGolApQl8Q01yfI1gvfEEwvgE1_WuaU4VtSpVOlBgXmm0zd6cNYnV2y5E3uYBpgyiquGvpir-W7OedswRJ5J\" alt=\"\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>NEW LOADING SCREENS<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>We have updated the loading screens with more recent and fan-favourite Titans!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https:\/\/lh5.googleusercontent.com\/-Xij8Xx7Hg1rDDzg3ywmvlqAkekLG54ttrDaTdlvOodS4LlQWAYFaJkGB3N64bcIvOE9sNcBbhNSjMiLZK7Cca6FYVtTkBp49bCHETPsf0N04a5-jdBeaoGGV2UXufHlWT_l9i4D\" alt=\"\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>NEW DAILY CALENDAR REWARDS<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>In 1.39, a new monthly-rolling login calendar will be available, with better rewards, and a new All Element Titan Token. This token can be redeemed at the ALL ELEMENT TITAN altar from within the Temple. This altar guarantees a 4* Titan with each use (please note: new players, and those returning to Dawn of Titans after a significant hiatus, may be presented with different calendars).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https:\/\/lh5.googleusercontent.com\/LeSg4oUOhV91XZjygLKvk2jfsx4i1XDU8aVRi3OIIv5FR41aphFhbqENpgMYeDu7HUoJgSAgbu6vFje3PkaARTHqn_qMP-P_SU-Ohzll1x0kLKPfg8cP1T_7b0UAfat7oz2j4FFJ\" alt=\"\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https:\/\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\/oG1W6nfpK4yrRm2lbmnVeJMLxBM_pobTj-rouA85lXjvATPignqVhP66jNqsh8E_2heOnQ_mHfK5_Gbfh4FQIF7bBau7ovNzv5d_7YiGmQ3PeUQKtYrqehO0pnpLSYcLqSTd27vE\" alt=\"\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"\/>\n\n