re Gold and Food for Castle Levels 1-19.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition, each Gold Vault and Granary will now store 25% more Gold and Food (Castle Levels 1-25). This value is even greater for lower Castle Levels.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Each Gold and Food treasury will now protect 25% more Gold and Food (Castle Levels 1-25). This value is even greater for lower Castle Levels.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>TUTORIAL AND NEW-PLAYER IMPROVEMENTS<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>A streamlined tutorial and new player experience has been implemented into 1.39. These changes will help the increasing number of new players integrate into Alliances, the League game and Events.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>ARENAS, MONUMENTS AND ADVENTURER\u2019S GUILD<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Several adjustments have been made to Titan Arenas, Titan Monuments and the Adventurer\u2019s Guild.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Titan Arenas now grant more Titan and Player XP:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"626\" height=\"269\" src=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/TitanArenaXP.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-681\" srcset=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/TitanArenaXP.png 626w, https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/TitanArenaXP-300x129.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 626px) 100vw, 626px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Titan Monuments will now <strong>always<\/strong> drop 3 Battle Drops. The Battle Drops for Titan Monuments have also been updated and improved.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition, Titan Monuments will now grant more Titan and Player XP:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"626\" height=\"228\" src=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/TitanMonumentXP.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-682\" srcset=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/TitanMonumentXP.png 626w, https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/TitanMonumentXP-300x109.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 626px) 100vw, 626px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Faction Adventures (weekly rotating Campaigns in the Adventurer&#8217;s Guild) now grant more Titan XP:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"471\" height=\"412\" src=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/AdventurersGuildXP.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-683\" srcset=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/AdventurersGuildXP.png 471w, https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/AdventurersGuildXP-300x262.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 471px) 100vw, 471px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>NEW TITANS<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>As the War Gods reach the end of their era, a new assembly of Titans with unique INVOKE effects will descend on the Shattered Kingdoms. These Titans have lain dormant across the realm since before the earth was shattered, but their return is now imminent. Make sure to check out our weekly blog posts for more information in the near future!&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>NEW APP ICON<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>We\u2019ve updated the store page for Dawn of Titans with new icons, promotional art and descriptions to better represent the game in 2020.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"608\" height=\"346\" src=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/AppIcon.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-684\" srcset=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/AppIcon.png 608w, https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/AppIcon-300x171.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p>We value your feedback on this new update, and we look forward to hearing from you across our official and unofficial social channels.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>And as always, we\u2019ll <em>see you on the battlefield!<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Titans! Dawn of Titans\u2019 new update &#8211; 1.39 &#8211; is gradually being released to all players, and will soon be available for all to download&hellip;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":685,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[5],"tags":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/MOTD_ConstructionFrenzy_04_DescS.png","_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/678"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=678"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/678\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":686,"href":"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/678\/revisions\/686"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/685"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=678"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http